STATE of Washington, Respondent,
v.
Cleon Orville MOEN, Petitioner. No. 96393-2 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, March 7, 2019.

ORDER

¶ 1 This case came before the Court on its March 7, 2019, En Banc Conference to consider the petition for review. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the petition for review is denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J. CHIEF JUSTICE
